  "keyFeatures": [
    "JSON/TypeScript-typed declarative field schema for building forms and layouts",
    "Automatic form state management with onChange, handler, and defaultValue",
    "Responsive 12-column grid system with phone/tablet/desktop breakpoints",
    "Built-in form validation with isInvalid, isDisabled, and isVisible callbacks",
    "Rich field types: Text, Combo, Items, Rating, Date, Slider, Tree, Dict, and more",
    "Layout types: Group, Paper, Expansion, Tabs, Hero, Outline, Condition",
    "ListTyped data grid with filters, pagination, sorting, chips, and row actions",
    "Scaffold2/3 for full Material Design app shell with sidebar navigation",
    "KanbanView for drag-and-drop board management",
    "WizardView for multi-step workflows with routing",
    "OneSlotFactory for custom UI-kit overrides without changing schemas",
    "Async hooks: useAsyncValue, useSinglerunAction, useQueuedAction, useAsyncProgress",
    "MVVM patterns: useCollection, useModel, useEntity",
    "Reactive programming: Subject, BehaviorSubject, EventEmitter, Source (MapReduce)",
    "Built-in router with guards, prefetch, unload, and redirect support",
    "Dependency injection: provide, inject, createServiceManager"
  ],
